{"tid":1457053,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HV7400車主Chiu Chi Wai盗竊大肚婆車牌","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:11:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:11:31.000Z","uid":41067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5d66a7a22726b0ce8bfa6ec9eaebc4750cf82680","tid":1457053,"uid":41067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:11:31.000Z","msg":"代友post<br />\n<br />\n(請廣傳) 此車(HV7400)車主Chiu Chi Wai因為星期五26/7/2019泊車阻住人(在貨櫃碼頭南路， 介乎ATL 與 二號貨櫃碼貨之間的迴旋處 ，附近一個沒街名的停車位置)阻住了其他車主，打了電話通知他，落到嚟又唔肯倒車，HV7400車主唔肯倒車之餘仲要發爛渣，拆除/盜竊了受影響者大肚婆的車牌，當時大肚婆不在埸，要靠其他車主告知，又因為佗住8個月身紀又行動不便，令到一位大肚婆收工都要週圍走去其他車房整番個全新嘅車牌。當晚致電HV7400車主，佢唔認係佢拆車牌，然後到29/7/2019星期一先打番嚟道歉, 毫無悔意。以下奉上他的罪証及車牌。已證實HV7400車主Chiu Chi Wai在一間叫YAMATO LOGISTICS (HK) LTD 番工，佢電話係91925048, 奉上大頭照幾張。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Azh3Sc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzh3Sc5.jpg&h=6c955225&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D0P2ojN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD0P2ojN.jpg&h=93190dd4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6DuUYS9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6DuUYS9.jpg&h=5ac25f02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y3LXWEQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY3LXWEQ.jpg&h=c705efd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hBm8iTb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhBm8iTb.jpg&h=833d5e9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5xEhWE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5xEhWE3.jpg&h=1c640992&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}